Additional third-party notices
==============================

This MIT License applies only to the LektorAI by Slawaspr0 application code
written for this project.

LektorAI by Slawaspr0 can install, call, launch or interoperate with external
TTS/STT engines, APIs, models, Python packages and command-line tools. Those
external components are not relicensed by this MIT License. They remain under
their own licenses, terms of service, model licenses and usage policies.

Users are responsible for using all external engines, models, generated audio,
voice samples, subtitles and video materials in accordance with the applicable
licenses, terms and local law.

If a distributed build bundles any third-party component, include that
component's full license text and required notices with the build.


Internet services
-----------------

Edge TTS and OpenAI TTS are external online services/APIs. LektorAI by
Slawaspr0 acts only as a client/launcher for them. Use of those services may be
subject to the providers' own terms, policies, availability, account
requirements and API requirements.


Chatterbox TTS
--------------

Chatterbox TTS is an external TTS engine by Resemble AI.

Project: https://github.com/resemble-ai/chatterbox
License: MIT License.

Chatterbox TTS is not owned by this project. If installed or used through
LektorAI by Slawaspr0, it remains licensed by its original authors under its own
license.


