-------------

OmniVoice is an external TTS engine.

Project: https://github.com/k2-fsa/OmniVoice
License: Apache License 2.0.

OmniVoice is not owned by this project. If installed or used through LektorAI by
Slawaspr0, it remains licensed by its original authors under its own license.


Piper TTS
---------

Piper TTS is an external TTS engine.

Project: https://github.com/OHF-Voice/piper1-gpl
License: GNU General Public License v3.0 or later.

Piper TTS is not owned by this project. If installed or used through LektorAI by
Slawaspr0, it remains licensed by its original authors under its own license.
Piper voice models may have their own licenses; review the license information
for the selected voice before redistribution or publication.


Coqui XTTS-v2 / Coqui AI TTS
----------------------------

Coqui AI TTS is an external TTS engine, and XTTS-v2 is an external model used by
that ecosystem.

Project: https://github.com/idiap/coqui-ai-TTS
Code license: Mozilla Public License 2.0.
XTTS-v2 model license: Coqui Public Model License.

Coqui AI TTS and XTTS-v2 are not owned by this project. If installed or used
through LektorAI by Slawaspr0, they remain licensed by their original authors
under their own licenses. The XTTS-v2 model license may include
non-commercial-use restrictions unless the user has separate commercial rights.


faster-whisper
--------------

faster-whisper is an external STT engine by SYSTRAN.

Project: https://github.com/SYSTRAN/faster-whisper
License: MIT License.

faster-whisper is not owned by this project. If installed or used through
LektorAI by Slawaspr0, it remains licensed by its original authors under its own
license. Speech recognition models used with faster-whisper may have their own
licenses and terms.


whisper.cpp
-----------

whisper.cpp is an external STT engine by the ggml authors.

Project: https://github.com/ggml-org/whisper.cpp
License: MIT License.

whisper.cpp is not owned by this project. If installed or used through LektorAI
by Slawaspr0, it remains licensed by its original authors under its own license.
Speech recognition models used with whisper.cpp may have their own licenses and
terms.


WhisperX
--------

WhisperX is an external STT engine.

Project: https://github.com/m-bain/whisperX
License: BSD 2-Clause License.

WhisperX is not owned by this project. If installed or used through LektorAI by
